Requirement to use  tool (gulp serve) and (gulp serve:dist):

1. NODE - Installed version : v4.3.0
2. GIT - git version 2.8.3.windows.1
3. GULP - [17:19:33] CLI version 3.9.1
4. BOWER - v1.8.0
5. NPM - v2.14.12

Clone this repo and install npm production dependencies:
    npm install --production

Make sure the computer has node & npm installed already.

To start (production):
    npm run start